            <div class="row justify-content-around gy-4">
                <h2 class="mission_title">Our Values</h2>
                <hr>
                <div class="col-lg-6 img-bg " data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100">
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="card" style="width: 100%;">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="card-text">Dhaka Choice Ltd has adopted patriotism, honesty, fair practice and
                                service to the nation as its core values, which act as the main basis in its
                                decision-making. These values have created a moral compass for everyone at the company
                                from the top management to ordinary employees and created the organizational culture
                                accordingly. The group always tries to be driven by these values and not to deviate from
                                them in any situation.</p>
                        </div>
